release.changelog:
* You can now save, view, or edit any website to Bookmarks via the dropdown menu.
* You can now view or clear the Browser History via the dropdown menu.
* The 'update available' error has been fixed on devices running Android 12 or earlier, even when weekly updates are made.
* We have reorganized the settings screen for easier access.
